Starlight Engine Replica.desc: A customized supercomputing W-Engine, specialized in aim support and ballistic calculations. Modified by Billy, it now looks like some sort of knock-off Starlight Knight figurine.
Starlight Engine Replica.name: Starlight Engine Replica

The Brimstone.desc: A W-Engine made for Soldier 11 by Obsidian Division. Its intense heat can be used to clear the entire battlefield.
The Brimstone.name: The Brimstone

[Vortex] Hatchet.desc: A frequency-converting W-Engine that can quickly generate excessive power and effectively increase its user's battle prowess.
[Vortex] Hatchet.name: [Vortex] Hatchet

The Vault.desc: A cost-effective W-Engine that can store energy, with improvements made to its internal space. This model is often used by Nicole.
The Vault.name: The Vault

Slice of Time.desc: A special W-Engine equipped with a high-speed camera module. The best choice for in-Hollow photography enthusiasts.
Slice of Time.name: Slice of Time

Bashful Demon.desc: An intricate W-Engine developed by Section 6 and later modified with extra features. It can control Ether particles to form an energy field. This model is favored by Soukaku.
Bashful Demon.name: Bashful Demon

[Lunar] Noviluna.desc: A high-capacity portable W-Engine that can collect dissipated energy from its surroundings, thus enhancing the combat effectiveness of its operator.
[Lunar] Noviluna.name: [Lunar] Noviluna

[Lunar] Decrescent.desc: A W-Engine with excellent sonic and thermal energy usage, capable of hitting its target with a double whammy.
[Lunar] Decrescent.name: [Lunar] Decrescent

Weeping Gemini.desc: A W-Engine produced by recycling abandoned Bangboo shells. Its electrode cores made of recycled metals can release high-voltage charges.
Weeping Gemini.name: Weeping Gemini

Cannon Rotor.desc: A high-performance supercomputing W-Engine, capable of collecting real-time battlefield data and equipped with mini cannons.
Cannon Rotor.name: Cannon Rotor

Rainforest Gourmet.desc: A consumer-class W-Engine launched by an exotic pet fan club to promote pet culture. Due to its cute appearance, it was once a very popular model.
Rainforest Gourmet.name: Rainforest Gourmet

Bunny Band.desc: A special W-Engine decorated with a fluffy bunny. However, it is just an imitation of the real animal.
Bunny Band.name: Bunny Band

Spring Embrace.desc: A special W-Engine equipped with a temperature regulator where residual heat generated by the W-Engine's high frequency is funneled into the hot springs on its surface.
Spring Embrace.name: Spring Embrace

Steel Cushion.desc: A supercomputing W-Engine equipped with a motion monitoring feature. Thanks to Nekomata's modifications, it perfectly matches the fast reflexes and combat maneuvers of feline Thirens.
Steel Cushion.name: Steel Cushion

The Restrained.desc: A special W-Engine with a powerful temperature control system. Modified by Lycaon, it has the capability to quickly create extremely cold environments.
The Restrained.name: The Restrained

Fusion Compiler.desc: The latest W-Engine that possesses a hypercalculation core. It can compile operational codes for machines at top speed. This model is favored by Grace.
Fusion Compiler.name: Fusion Compiler

[Magnetic Storm] Bravo.desc: A damage-type W-Engine that features an enhanced movement detection module that can quickly alter its output intensity to optimize battle efficiency.
[Magnetic Storm] Bravo.name: [Magnetic Storm] Bravo

Original Transmorpher.desc: An epic W-Engine favored by Starlight Knight fans. Its high popularity and scarcity marketing strategy have caused an influx of knock-offs.
Original Transmorpher.name: Original Transmorpher

[Reverb] Mark II.desc: A standardized W-Engine with balanced performance that enhances its owner's and their teammates' combat effectiveness in all aspects.
[Reverb] Mark II.name: [Reverb] Mark II

Big Cylinder.desc: A powerful protection-type W-Engine, characterized by thick oil cylinders that ceaselessly roar inside it. It can provide sufficient power for heavy machinery.
Big Cylinder.name: Big Cylinder

[Vortex] Revolver.desc: An energy-storage type W-Engine with a unique operation circuit. It will absorb scattered energy up to a certain amount before unleashing it all at once.
[Vortex] Revolver.name: [Vortex] Revolver

Deep Sea Visitor.desc: A high-power W-Engine that possesses efficient freezing capabilities and high damage output. This model is often used by Ellen.
Deep Sea Visitor.name: Deep Sea Visitor

Riot Suppressor Mark VI.desc: The latest tactical W-Engine used by Public Security's elite Hollow squads, possessing a powerful Ether energy source. It's Zhu Yuan's favored model.
Riot Suppressor Mark VI.name: Riot Suppressor Mark VI

Demara Battery Mark II.desc: A customized W-Engine that focuses on energy storage, modified to improve its energy capacity. This model is often used by Anby.
Demara Battery Mark II.name: Demara Battery Mark II

Hellfire Gears.desc: A functional W-Engine with ultra-high power capacity. Modified by Koleda, its energy level has almost exceeded the safety limit.
Hellfire Gears.name: Hellfire Gears

[Identity] Base.desc: A W-Engine with a component structure adjusted according to specific parameters. It can enhance the defensive capabilities of those who have a certain style of combat.
[Identity] Base.name: [Identity] Base

[Reverb] Mark III.desc: A special W-Engine that features motion capture algorithms, which enhance the overall combat competency of your squad.
[Reverb] Mark III.name: [Reverb] Mark III

Starlight Engine.desc: A damage-type W-Engine made of special Etheric matter. When its user is attacked, it builds up energy.
Starlight Engine.name: Starlight Engine

[Identity] Inflection.desc: A functional W-Engine that specializes in energy conversion. It can analyze combat environments and generate special sounds to disrupt the enemy's offense.
[Identity] Inflection.name: [Identity] Inflection

Steam Oven.desc: A high-power W-Engine that boasts a cutting-edge energy conversion system. It collects excess heat and supplies it to the steamer.
Steam Oven.name: Steam Oven

Drill Rig - Red Axis.desc: Originally a rev-enhanced W-Engine, it has been modified by Anton with the most expensive rotary drill parts that allow it to exceed its output limits.
Drill Rig - Red Axis.name: Drill Rig - Red Axis

Weeping Cradle.desc: A special W-Engine with multiple layers embedded inside. It can quickly recharge special Bangboo and custom-made combat equipment. This model is favored by Rina.
Weeping Cradle.name: Weeping Cradle

[Magnetic Storm] Alpha.desc: A special W-Engine that can analyze the target's weak spots through real-time calculations.
[Magnetic Storm] Alpha.name: [Magnetic Storm] Alpha

Kaboom the Cannon.desc: A support W-Engine propelled by jets that is both mobile and impactful, it can traverse the entire battlefield providing combat buffs.
Kaboom the Cannon.name: Kaboom the Cannon

Electro-Lip Gloss.desc: This damage-type W-Engine boasts a built-in current transformer, and automatically attracts electrically sensitive objects around the operator and deals additional damage to them.
Electro-Lip Gloss.name: Electro-Lip Gloss

[Reverb] Mark I.desc: A special W-Engine featuring a built-in sonic generator that boosts its damage output.
[Reverb] Mark I.name: [Reverb] Mark I

[Vortex] Arrow.desc: A tactical W-Engine that locates enemies using high-frequency sound waves. Its aiming aid can make its operator's precision attack more deadly.
[Vortex] Arrow.name: [Vortex] Arrow

[Lunar] Pleniluna.desc: A W-Engine that prioritizes damage output over noise reduction. It can indiscriminately deal considerable damage to all units nearby.
[Lunar] Pleniluna.name: [Lunar] Pleniluna

Housekeeper.desc: An enhanced W-Engine with a high rotation speed. A chainsaw has been integrated into its shaft. This model is often used by Corin.
Housekeeper.name: Housekeeper

Unfettered Game Ball.desc: A new supercomputing W-Engine, featuring cutting-edge integrated chips that dynamically monitor the battlefield and provide tactical analysis for the user.
Unfettered Game Ball.name: Unfettered Game Ball

Street Superstar.desc: A custom-made W-Engine designed for urban music lovers. It sacrifices heat dissipation components for improved sound quality.
Street Superstar.name: Street Superstar

Precious Fossilized Core.desc: A special W-Engine whose outer shell is made of composite Etheric matter that effectively absorbs impact, and turns it against the enemy.
Precious Fossilized Core.name: Precious Fossilized Core

[Magnetic Storm] Charlie.desc: A high-capacity W-Engine that features a built-in generator, which allows it to keep a stable storage of electrical power.
[Magnetic Storm] Charlie.name: [Magnetic Storm] Charlie

Six Shooter.desc: A special W-Engine modeled after a revolver. It can load bullet-shaped condensed Ether batteries, which release a great amount of power when fired.
Six Shooter.name: Six Shooter

Roaring Ride.desc: An energy W-Engine modded from spare parts of a truck's engine. It converts the original cylinder into an energy storage unit, which is highly advantageous.
Roaring Ride.name: Roaring Ride

Peacekeeper - Specialized.desc: A defensive W-Engine independently researched and created by Public Security which simplifies the offensive components to enhance the energy conversion ability in its shield.
Peacekeeper - Specialized.name: Peacekeeper - Specialized

Gilded Blossom.desc: A W-Engine with a grandiose and luxurious appearance equipped with a premium Ether-powered anti-theft device. Actually used to provide the equipper with energy.
Gilded Blossom.name: Gilded Blossom

Sharpened Stinger.desc: A deadly W-Engine from unknown sources, modified personally by Jane Doe with the intent to deal severe physical damage and Anomaly.
Sharpened Stinger.name: Sharpened Stinger

Ice-Jade Teapot.desc: A custom stun W-Engine made for an Automaton referencing the combat style and abilities of one. Energy is stored within, then lashes outwards upon conversion.
Ice-Jade Teapot.name: Ice-Jade Teapot

Tusks of Fury.desc: A versatile W-Engine based on a motorcycle tire that Big Daddy made for Caesar.
Tusks of Fury.name: Tusks of Fury

Flamemaker Shaker.desc: Modified by Burnice, this W-Engine uses a special fuel as its power source to boost combustion performance to the max.
Flamemaker Shaker.name: Flamemaker Shaker

Blazing Laurel.desc: A violent W-Engine that can ignite flames with a siphon. It deals simple and crude burn damage, encouraging relentless, bone-crushing follow-up attacks.
Blazing Laurel.name: Blazing Laurel

Timeweaver.desc: A new model of supercomputing W-Engine custom-made by HSO Section 6, equipped with the most elite calculation and analysis functions.
Timeweaver.name: Timeweaver

Marcato Desire.desc: Gather 'round, mortals! Turn up the music!
Marcato Desire.name: Marcato Desire

Zanshin Herb Case.desc: Bitterness and pain beget hope, and he devours them all.
Zanshin Herb Case.name: Zanshin Herb Case

Hailstorm Shrine.desc: Hail falls before the shrine, waking her. The blizzard is coming.
Hailstorm Shrine.name: Hailstorm Shrine

Item_Weapon_A_1351_Name.desc: An energy W-Engine modded from spare parts of a truck's engine. It converts the original cylinder into an energy storage unit, which is highly advantageous.
Item_Weapon_A_1351_Name.name: Item_Weapon_A_1351_Name

Heartstring Nocturne.desc: The sound of the strings, sharp as blades, cut through the night, protecting the one.
Heartstring Nocturne.name: Heartstring Nocturne

Elegant Vanity.desc: Underneath the radiant splendor, her genuine self has never been hidden.
Elegant Vanity.name: Elegant Vanity

Box Cutter.desc: An energy W-Engine modded from spare parts of a truck's engine. It converts the original cylinder into an energy storage unit, which is highly advantageous.
Box Cutter.name: Box Cutter

Flight of Fancy.desc: A bird landed on the windowsill, scattering starlight from its tail feathers.
Flight of Fancy.name: Flight of Fancy

Myriad Eclipse.desc: Shadowed by darkness at every step, he laid bare his heart to kindle a single, flickering flame.
Myriad Eclipse.name: Myriad Eclipse

Tremor Trigram Vessel.desc: Pressing acupoints is like cooking. Striking the fatal acupoint is like setting the stove on fire, bringing disaster.
Tremor Trigram Vessel.name: Tremor Trigram Vessel
